-- T11 Tou Tou: camp randomization, per-species bosses, empower flags, variation-scaled counts
-- Generated migration. Run AFTER '730000001 T11 Tou Tou Mobs.sql' and
-- '730001001 T11 Tou Tou Generators and Placements.sql' (this file re-owns rows they seed).
--
-- Camp design: each camp gen spawns 1 boss (always) + a random mix of same-species mobs.
-- Total count = int 50103 (base 6 = boss + 5 mobs) + (landblock variation - int 50104 baseline 11),
-- applied by ApplyVariationScaledSpawnCount() in WorldObject_Generators.cs.

